subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Fans rallied around the qualifier Jessica Pegula, the 21-year-old daughter of the Bills’ and Sabres' owner Terry Pegula, as she captured her first victory in the main draw of a Grand Slam event.
